item.title: End of an Era: The Pay-off and Dangers of High Expectations
item.description: When I moved into University in September 2021, I solidified the idea that I will get a First Class degree, no matter what it takes. It’s been almost 4 years since then, and today I have been notified that I have obtained that grade.
